<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM1.4.10">
<l>maittaṭaṅ kaṇṇi yacōtai taṉmakaṉukkivai</l>
<l>yottaṉa colli yuraitta māṟṟa moḷiputtūr</l>
<l>vittakaṉ viṭṭu cittaṉ viritta tamiḻivai</l>
<l>yettaṉai yumcolla valla varkkiṭa rillaiyē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>There is no affliction for those who are able to say all of these Tamil [verses]</l>
<l>that were written by Viṣṇu Cittaṉ, sage of bright Puttūr,</l>
<l>with these words that were spoken that resemble those</l>
<l>spoken by Yaśodā, with koel [lined] wide eyes, for her son.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
